snippet.title: The Spy Who Loved Me N64 - Preview (4K 60FPS)
snippet.description:
The Spy Who Loved Me is a full campaign mod for GoldenEye that aims to recreate the original film from 1977. Please keep in mind this is a work in progress. I'm showcasing the 11 playable levels in this build that was given to me, this time on emulator instead of real hardware.

Thanks to José García for the thumbnail art!

Emulator tutorial: https://youtu.be/8mL0I__VMec
Custom level install tutorial: https://youtu.be/8mL0I__VMec?t=252
Check out this ROM hack running on original hardware: https://youtu.be/lr5t4sp5MXE

You can download the demo here, keep in mind it's not the one being showcased here at the moment and features only 3 levels: http://n64vault.com/ge-campaigns:the-spy-who-loved-me-64
